if else  in python

if else sabhi programming language main hote hai
because it is necessary iske bina coading krna possible nhi hai

example apka code 2 taraf ja rha hai kuch situation ke karan 
to iss ko branching  bolte hai branches develop ho rhe hai 

for example login program and identation

agar kis ne login page main correct information feed kre to  to usko credential dike ge
 
else error show kra ga


jab bhi brnching hota hai to use handle kne ke leya if-else use hote hai

for example login program and identation
email -> random123@gmail.com
password ->1234 

agar iske alava password and email use hoge to error show kre ga



email = input("enter email")
password = input("enter password")

if email =='random123@gmail.com' and password == '1234':
  print("Welcome")
else:
  print("error")

-----------------output ------------------
enter emailrandom123@gmail.com
enter password1234
Welcome


-----------another output-----------------
